Sentencas: Misfit-type Ca3-xLaxCo4O9+delta (x=0, 0.3) oxides were synthesised to be evaluated as possible cathode materials for proton conducting fuel cells (PCFCs) based on BaCe0.9Y0.1O3-delta (BCY10) dense ceramic electrolyte.
Titulo: Ca3-xLaxCo4O9+δ (x=0, 0.3): New cobaltite materials as cathodes for proton conducting solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity value of Ca2.7La0.3Co4O9+delta (sigma approximate to 53 S cm(-1) at 600 degrees C) is in the range of usually required value for a cathode application (about 50-100 S cm(-1))
Titulo: Ca3-xLaxCo4O9+δ (x=0, 0.3): New cobaltite materials as cathodes for proton conducting solid oxide fuel cell
